data.description: Woodbury School District 833 – South Washington County!  The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, providing a sense of flow throughout the home while also featuring a two-sided fireplace for added ambiance.  The spacious master suite is a retreat in itself, offering a lounging area, private bathroom, large closet, and plenty of windows for natural light.  The additional bedrooms and loft are versatile and perfect for family members, guests, or creating a home office – all on the upper level!  There's also a dedicated upstairs laundry room.  With 2.25 bathrooms, morning routines and entertaining guests are made easy.  Step outside onto your private patio, perfect for al fresco dining, gardening, or simply relaxing with a book. The community may offer additional outdoor amenities for you to enjoy. Woodbury offers an abundance of recreational parks, shopping centers, dining options, cultural attractions, and easy access to major transportation routes.
